gametitle=Shadow of the Colossus (PAL, SCES-53326) [CRC 0F0C4A9C]
comment=BISECT test5 - FULL v17 right-aim with Tramp B relocated to safe padding

// Bisection showed 0x001A5248 is used by the game during boot.
// Move Tramp B into the confirmed-safe 0x001A4984 padding region,
// right after Tramp A ends at 0x001A499C.
//
// Layout:
//   0x001A4984..0x001A499C   Tramp A (7 words, unchanged)
//   0x001A49A0..0x001A49CC   Tramp B (12 words, MOVED from 0x001A5248)
//
// Hook B's jump target changes: 0x08069492 -> 0x08069268 (j 0x001A49A0).
// Tramp B's internal code is unchanged (its return j 0x01176ABC is absolute).

// ==== Hook A: pad-read ==================================================
patch=1,EE,0001ACD44,word,08069261
patch=1,EE,0001ACD48,word,92420107

// ==== Trampoline A body at 0x001A4984 (v17 right-aim, 7 words) ==========
